description:
Just Dance is a 2009 music Rhythm game and the 1st game in the Just Dance franchise. Like other Just Dance games, you try to match the dancer's movements. It was heavily criticized for its poor motion tracking, and I agree. The game was expanded from the min-game dancing routines in Rayman Rabbids TV Party. I'm playing the game until I get at least 10,000 points for each song, with some having 15,000 points for the crown. Then I'll post a longplay of every song which will likely be speed up due to the amount of copyrighted material. This video covers the 2004 Fatboy Slim remix of the 1960 song "Jin Go Lo Ba" by Babatunde Olatunji.
